      <Label text="LEGAL &amp; PRIVACY" font="font:LargeBoldSystemFont" color="#DAAB2D" width="1000" />
      <Rectangle width="60" height="2" color="#DAAB2D" translation="[0, 50]" />

      <!-- Content -->
      <Label id="legalText"
             text="By using the T.O.N.Y. Roku Channel, you agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.&#10;&#10;When you use Device Linking to sign into your account, we generate a unique Device ID and collect your IP address to secure the connection to your topofnewyork.com account.&#10;&#10;We also collect playback analytics to allow you to resume episodes where you left off.&#10;&#10;To view our complete Privacy Policy, Terms of Service, and learn how we manage and protect your data, please visit:&#10;&#10;https://topofnewyork.com/privacy" 
